        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1516,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1516,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01D8FGKYm7V1raQ2pAj32p29\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic scheduling tool time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling app\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting time finder\\\",\\n    \\\"distributed team scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate scheduling conflicts\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional**: People actively searching for scheduling solutions (\\\"meeting scheduler\\\", \\\"scheduling tool\\\")\\n- **Problem-focused**: Teams struggling with the core pain point (\\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\", \\\"eliminate scheduling conflicts\\\")\\n- **Awareness keywords**: Broader searches that capture teams exploring options (\\\"team scheduling app\\\", \\\"calendar coordination software\\\")\\n\\nThe mix should help your ads appear when remote teams and project managers are actively looking for a solution like yours. Want to adjust any of these or explore different angles?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1653,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":224,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
