            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01NWi2qo2HJJF9TV3EjDCKft\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great! Let me refresh these with snappier, more punchy language that'll really grab attention.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Save 15 Hours Weekly\\\",\\n    \\\"Zero Back-and-Forth\\\",\\n    \\\"Auto Time Zone Match\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ Teams Rely On Us\\\",\\n    \\\"Free Trial—No Card\\\",\\n    \\\"One Click. Done.\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"Service catalog\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Smart Calendar Sync\\\",\\n      \\\"Instant Suggestions\\\",\\n      \\\"Global Team Support\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese hit harder and cut the fluff. How are these feeling?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2942,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":171,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
