            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1614,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01CwUjZPfCTrDerR838jZDkG\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic calendar scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"timezone meeting coordinator\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting time finder for global teams\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar sync for remote work\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional**: \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\", \\\"automatic calendar scheduling software\\\", \\\"team scheduling across time zones\\\"\\n- **Problem-focused**: \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\", \\\"timezone meeting coordinator\\\"\\n- **Awareness & comparison**: \\\"best scheduling tool for distributed teams\\\", \\\"meeting time finder for global teams\\\"\\n- **Broad solution keywords**: \\\"calendar sync for remote work\\\"\\n\\nThey're designed to capture searches from project managers and remote team leads actively looking for scheduling solutions. Ready to move forward with these, or would you like me to adjust any?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1146,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":246,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
