            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01HWy5HcMagKgU2okvaHAyaA\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling app\\\",\\n    \\\"automated meeting scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"best time for meeting tool\\\",\\n    \\\"distributed team scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"stop scheduling back and forth\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional keywords** (people ready to buy): \\\"meeting scheduling tool\\\", \\\"calendar coordination software\\\", \\\"team scheduling app\\\"\\n- **Problem-focused keywords** (people searching for solutions): \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\", \\\"stop scheduling back and forth\\\"\\n- **Awareness keywords** (broader searches): \\\"automated meeting scheduler\\\", \\\"distributed team scheduling\\\"\\n\\nThe mix ensures your ads show up when remote teams are actively looking for scheduling solutions. Want to adjust any of these or add keywords for specific industries or use cases?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1837,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":230,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
