            "size": 1512,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01GcRirnErtNwJLqGqSPkrGS\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"automated meeting scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate scheduling conflicts\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional keywords** (1-3): People actively looking to buy a scheduling solution\\n- **Problem-focused keywords** (4-6): Teams frustrated with current scheduling pain points\\n- **Awareness keywords** (7-8): Broader searches from teams exploring options\\n\\nThe mix should help you capture people at different stages—from those actively searching for a tool to those just realizing they have a scheduling problem.\\n\\nWhat would you like to adjust? We can swap any of these out, add location-specific keywords if you target certain regions, or refine the focus.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1663,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":241,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
