            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1548,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01DPKuUgcUg7CbisuXCZ2MmC\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great idea! Let me refresh those with more personality and humor that'll stand out in the feed.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Scheduling Without the Chaos\\\",\\n    \\\"Finally, a Calendar That Gets It\\\",\\n    \\\"No More 'Works for You?' Texts\\\",\\n    \\\"Meeting Time Roulette? Never Again\\\",\\n    \\\"Your Team's New Best Friend\\\",\\n    \\\"Timezone Drama? We Got This\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect calendars, skip the Slack threads. We find times that work for everyone instantly.\\\",\\n    \\\"Used by 2,000+ teams. Save 15 hours weekly on scheduling. Try free today.\\\",\\n    \\\"Tired of endless meeting coordination? Get optimal times in seconds. Start now.\\\",\\n    \\\"Distributed teams trust us. Automatic scheduling across all time zones. No more conflicts.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese have way more personality! They speak directly to the pain points your audience actually feels—the endless back-and-forth, the timezone headaches, the meeting chaos. The humor should help you stand out against more corporate competitors.\\n\\nWant to adjust the tone further, or shall we keep these and move forward with your campaign setup?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2982,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":275,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
