        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1751,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1751,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Wa6j65zMGctKnMLpJF57zV\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling automation\\\",\\n    \\\"distributed team meeting planner\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic calendar coordinator\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting time finder for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"timezone meeting scheduler\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target the exact pain points your customers are searching for:\\n\\n- **High-intent transactional keywords** (keywords 1, 2, 4, 8): People actively looking to buy or try a scheduling solution\\n- **Problem-focused keywords** (keywords 3, 5, 7): Remote teams and distributed companies searching for solutions to their specific timezone challenges\\n- **Solution-oriented keywords** (keywords 6): People searching for automation to eliminate manual coordination\\n\\n**Want to refine these?**\\n- Add more location-based keywords (e.g., \\\"meeting scheduler for Europe\\\" or \\\"timezone coordinator for Asia-Pacific teams\\\")?\\n- Shift toward more budget-conscious searches (e.g., \\\"free meeting scheduler\\\")?\\n- Focus more on the pain point (e.g., \\\"stop scheduling conflicts\\\" or \\\"eliminate meeting coordination\\\")?\\n\\nLet me know what resonates!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1844,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":305,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
